    "id": 1,
    "level": 1,
    "title": "我的一天",
    "titleEn": "My Day",
    "text": "我每天六点起床。早上我喝水，吃米饭和鸡蛋。八点我去学校。老师很好，同学也很好。晚上我回家看书。",
    "translation": "I get up at six every day. In the morning I drink water and eat rice and eggs. At eight I go to school. The teacher is good, and my classmates are good too. In the evening I go home and read.",
